    # Friday AI 🤖

Friday AI is a personal voice assistant project built using Python on Ubuntu Linux.

## Features
- Voice commands
- Open applications
- Take screenshots
- Text-to-speech
- Speech recognition
- AI chatbot support

## Technologies Used
- Python
- PyAutoGUI
- SpeechRecognition
- Piper TTS
- Linux Ubuntu

